102
00:06:33,522 --> 00:06:34,144
Oh můj Bože!

103
00:06:34,231 --> 00:06:37,530
Tae-In! Tae-In!

104
00:06:38,901 --> 00:06:41,315
Kde jsi, Tae-In?

105
00:06:48,610 --> 00:06:52,937
